A4. Image and Environment Specifications
To minimize "Cold Start" times, the inference image was optimized for size and startup speed.
Base Layer: python:3.13-slim (chosen for the smallest secure footprint).
Core Libraries: ultralytics, fastapi, uvicorn, prometheus-client.
Model Weight Optimization: Weights were baked into the image layer to ensure immediate availability upon pod initialization.
Final Image Size: ~800 MB (Compressed).
